The '''Sudan Davis Cup team''' was a team that represented [[Sudan]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition. The team was governed by the [[Sudan Lawn Tennis Association]]. They have not competed since [[2001 Davis Cup|2001]].
==History== Sudan competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1994 Davis Cup|1994]]. Their best result was seventh in Group III in their debut year.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.daviscup.com/en/teams/team.aspx?id=SUD|title=Davis Cup - Teams|website=www.daviscup.com}}</ref>
